flowchart TB
    Client([Client])
    API[Payment API<br/>validate + idempotency]
    Orchestrator[Payment Orchestrator<br/>Saga: risk, auth, capture]
    IdemCache[(Idempotency Cache<br/>key-value store)]
    Risk[Risk Service]
    PSP([External PSP<br/>Stripe / Adyen])
    Ledger[(Ledger<br/>append-only<br/>double-entry log)]
    Recon[Reconciliation Job]

    Client -->|charge req| API
    API <-->|check + write| IdemCache
    API --> Orchestrator
    Orchestrator --> Risk
    Orchestrator -->|authorize / capture| PSP
    Orchestrator -->|debit + credit| Ledger
    PSP -.->|3DS / async webhook| Orchestrator
    Recon -->|daily diff| Ledger
    Recon <-->|settlement report| PSP

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client,PSP external
    class API,Orchestrator,Risk,Recon service
    class IdemCache,Ledger store
